## The Global Speaker

**Master the Stage. Command the Screen.**

This three-tier program is the definitive training suite for professionals operating in a hybrid, international landscape. We move beyond "public speaking" to develop **Bimodal Fluency**: the ability to transition seamlessly between the physical boardroom and the virtual frame.

